object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM operations.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = 'ACX'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM operations.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = 'ACX'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)

select distinct
metal_aeas.source_name,
metal_aeas.load_type,
metal_aeas.system_id,
metal_aeas.parent_id,
metal_aeas.cmm_container,
metal_aeas.id,
metal_aeas.assessment_id,
metal_aeas.solution_id,
metal_aeas.solution_name,
metal_aeas.business_function,
metal_aeas.assessed_entity,
metal_aeas.category,
metal_aeas.score,
metal_aeas.score_percentile,
metal_aeas.normalized_score,
metal_aeas.recommended_action_description,
metal_aeas.recommended_action_code,
metal_aeas.conclusion_description,
metal_aeas.conclusion_code,
metal_aeas.score_date,
metal_aeas.assesment_detail,
metal_aeas.error,
metal_aeas.row_id,
current_batch.batch_id
FROM metal.acx_ea_assessment_summary metal_aeas
CROSS JOIN current_batch
WHERE parent_id = 'EmbeddedAnalyticsReport-542492113-1524598694'
ORDER BY 
metal_aeas.system_id,
metal_aeas.parent_id,
metal_aeas.cmm_container,
metal_aeas.id;

object.customQuery:
SELECT
    acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_id,
    acx_ea_assessment_summary_batch_id,
    acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_md5checksum,
    acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_effective_end_datetime,
    system_id,
    parent_id,
    cmm_container,
    id
FROM bronze.acx_ea_assessment_summary
WHERE acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
  AND parent_id= 'EmbeddedAnalyticsReport-542492113-1524598694'
ORDER BY system_id, cmm_container;

fields.expression:

  NOT ISNULL(score_date) AND score_date != '',
  TO_CHAR(
    TO_DATE(SUBSTR(score_date, 1, 19), 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'),
